Shiritori [Shee-ree-toh-ree] is a japanese word chain game that involves kana
This game takes inspiration from that but using english words and letters
This is a two player game, the first person to play will be given at random
If your word ends with a letter, the next player will have to come up with a word with that letter at the beginning
If you make two mistakes, the other person will get a chance to steal your point